    <title>Important bug with pistons</title>
    <link>https://forum.moparisthebest.com/t/important-bug-with-pistons/401776</link>
    <description>I know me making everyone aware of this bug will not end well, but im just going to make you all aware anyway...

here is a diagram of a piston and lever &#39;paradox&#39; as i call it

[] = piston
| = lever
+ = redstone wire


++[]|
+    +
++++

The lever when activated will be pushed by the piston, sure thats what happens with every block, but this special setup will crash the server from then on and everytime you startup the server, so beware (and i know some of you will exploit this) of this bug and i hope this gets fixed by the time bukkit updates so we dont have some person trying this on moparcraft.</description>
    
